Package: EUPPB
Type: Package
Title: European PostProcessing Benchmark Data Downloader
Version: 0.0-1
Date: 2021-12-02
Author: Reto Stauffer
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Reto", family = "Stauffer", role = c("cre" "aut"), email = "Reto.Stauffer@uibk.ac.at",
                    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3798-5507")))
Description: Provides access to the European PostProcessing Benchmark Project
    data set. Data is provided as grib version 1; thus the libeccodes-dev
    is required to build/install the package (to compile the C code contained
    within the R package).
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Suggetsts: ncdf4
License: GPL-2
